com4j.tlbimp

Class IndentingWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Writer
      • java.io.PrintWriter
        • com4j.tlbimp.IndentingWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, Appendable, AutoCloseable

    public class IndentingWriter
extends PrintWriter
    PrintWriter with a little additional capability.

    Specifically,

    1. Indentation.
    2. Printing comma-separated tokens.
    3. Buffering the certain portion of the output and canceling it later.
    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi (kk@kohsuke.org), Michael Schnell (scm, (C) 2008, Michael-Schnell@gmx.de)
